"ml.png", "id": "502579852256353", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036644_502579858923019_3842705229132857953_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=U7KEWdISYXcQ7kNvgFYUSPg&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBzMEmkg0dItCgVSuxKUKnSQIo5EtJuo8h7xSM9wfruNg&oe=66FA8406"}, {"file_name": "landscape.png", "id": "465213706424419", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003266_465213709757752_680111565771229398_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=aDcUpXQIQPgQ7kNvgH_wX2I&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB8fRc1CQui7QZJPM5HR-AMd9PDuAeh-Tc6PsG0_LiPVw&oe=66FAA02E"}]}, "id": "695307962768721", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "4.png", "id": "964615488773393", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982581_964615495440059_2784752763184915334_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=56M77XNSgbAQ7kNvgEdko8v&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB0Xz6U8UMOVXxn6nqe_lWFHitOmiqnqy8OoZtd-h4uKw&oe=66FA9DEA"}, {"file_name": "2.png", "id": "1943374952743027", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974836_1943374956076360_2484593514118294358_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KLXGJt0CEJUQ7kNvgHOlo2U&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBkD0EETHF27P5n9qlqWkY-q0wJ-HvvRFFtt4vkx3BldA&oe=66FA9B82"}, {"file_name": "1.png", "id": "445060168517426", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75462964_445060171850759_5520915542327767111_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xqNp6E-JrQQQ7kNvgFx8ZSp&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC1E-JEJHZdX_JJ17xre1BsNvz8y1o2RK13me62IfUM0Q&oe=66FA8804"}, {"file_name": "5.png", "id": "467916352871409", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003282_467916356204742_1871921057092171900_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=L8iTCvTGvlMQ7kNvgE4uz-u&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDexJi2AmJdYGlUT0j6u52BXCpwQ0Vc5w5udexwaXXDPQ&oe=66FAA4E2"}, {"file_name": "3.png", "id": "1934382610375855", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974473_1934382613709188_7156337812617042679_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NnxzZH0sP7cQ7kNvgHgOHqU&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAhNIL8gWrsccZpTTtuddy4TCYgkv0_H4NzaviXtT8Reg&oe=66FA8EF3"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "landscape.png", "id": "1524760081483769", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974531_1524760084817102_6497712644828891067_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=b80v2svgAu8Q7kNvgEhKo_J&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCy2gVbqFKcePiCMk2r_hSW_Z_k07UzxVlGYkKffKC0xg&oe=66FA8DEF"}, "display_name": "Mystery Box VR: Hidden Secrets", "keywords": [], "long_description": " AN IMMERSIVE VR PUZZLE EXPERIENCE\nInteract with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. Crack enigmas and collect hidden puzzle tiles on a random side of the boxes.\n\nYou won't be able to compare reality with fiction.\n\n# DISCOVER INVENTIONS\nOnce you unlock all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and discover a brief history of an invention.\n\nIt's not always easy to escape the room, so use all your IQ to crack the riddles. There's a logic behind all of them, even where it seems it's not!\n\n# IMMERSIVE SOUNDTRACK\nPlay the game with your headphones to get immersed in this amazing adventure.\n\n# HINTS\nGot stuck on some enigma? No worries, you can still get a helpful hint! You can also get in touch with me in case you really can't make it through a riddle, I'll be glad to help ;)\n\n# MULTILANGUAGE\nAvailable in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.\n\nThe game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device", "short_description": "A VR escape room game where you have to solve intriguing riddles to open boxes and discover nice stories about popular inventions!"}, 